                        <interp inst="t18460817-name-1201" type="surname" value="LAMBERT"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18460817-name-1201" type="given" value="HENRY"></interp>HENRY LAMBERT</persName>
                  </hi>. I am in the prosecutor's service. The prisoner came to the shop and asked the price of a piece of pork—I showed her a piece, and told her the price was 6 1/2 <hi rend="italic">d</hi>. a pound, and I would weigh it outside—she was inside the shop—I told her to bring it out—she brought it out, and walked away with it—I made some inquiry of my master—I went, but could not see her—I got a policeman, and went to Forrest-gate, where she lives—the po<lb></lb>liceman went in, and came out with her—I saw the pork—it was the same piece I hadshown her—she was brought back, and she said she would pay my roaster for it.</p>
